      "name": "Bench-scale hemolysis validation against FDA pump experimental data",
      "description": "CFD-predicted hemolysis index compared against published FDA generic pump experimental measurements at 5 flow-speed operating points. Mean absolute error 38%; prediction intervals overlap experimental uncertainty bands at only 2 of 5 points. Validation insufficient for MRL 5 requirements."
    },
