    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-vv40-review-board",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Despite model risk level 5 requirements, the assessment team accepted the package provisionally based on the Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification results and the screening sensitivity study that identified flow rate and rotational speed as dominant hemolysis predictors. Six credibility factors remain not-assessed and seven assessed factors fall below required levels. Corrective action plan required prior to regulatory submission. Provisional acceptance granted to allow parallel device testing to proceed.",
